<inglise> Whereas the harm suffered by the inhabitants is more serious than they and the Member State concerned can make good unaided, and whereas Community assistance for this region is therefore required; </inglise>
<eesti> elanike kannatatav kahju on suurem, kui nad ise ja asjaomane liikmesriik suudaksid v&auml;lise abita k&otilde;rvaldada, mist&otilde;ttu k&otilde;nealune piirkond vajab &uuml;henduse abi; </eesti>
